{
  "texts": [
    "Same format as in b.",
    "We re-clustered LC types based on their connections to postsynaptic partners (rows differ from the ordering in b).",
    "Because this connectome dataset is from a female fruit fly, it may miss important sexually dimorphic, courtship-relevant connections to downstream areas of the male fruit fly.",
    "contribute to behaviour; we share our model and code (https://github.",
    "com/murthylab/one2one-mapping) with the community to inspire future experiments and models."
  ]
}